{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>You are a victim</strong> of circumstances in a winter forest, where every step echoes in the silence. Will you be able to find the way out, or will you remain in this silent nightmare forever?<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707040/extras/2eng.gif?t=1735952778\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What awaits you there.. or who?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>KRAMPEN</strong> is a digital horror-adventure game in which you will immerse yourself in a winter forest and help a lost soul regain a piece of itself. Uncover all the secrets that go beyond the gaming experience and discover the truth about the main character!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707040/extras/1.gif?t=1735952778\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The winter forest is deeper than it seems..</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">..it remembers all your deeds. The further you go into the forest, the more <span class=\"bb_strike\">firewood</span> there is. You will encounter a talking bush, a drunken stone, a psychologist fish, and many others. What secrets does the mysterious winter forest hold, once a witness to brutal violence, leaving its marks on the pristine canvas of winter?<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2707040/extras/3.gif?t=1735952778\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>This place is filled with a dark atmosphere of confusion and anxiety..</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The End?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2707040/0bc4a551c5e87858419aa668783ee55fa15007c3.jpg"},{"name":"Truth","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2707040/a315f49c0f25605f8cc2422e27f25f8c1992f6